PrecisEnactment of an ORDER PROHIBITING ENTRY ON CERTAIN LANDS IN THE YUKON TERRITORY (1999, No. 2, KLUANE FIRST NATION, Y.T.) - which prohibits staking mineral claims or prospecting for precious minerals on lands which may be required for the settlement of land claims made by the Kluane First Nation people.
